'''配水庫'''（英文：'''Service reservoir'''）是一種[[水庫|水庫]]，用作儲存已處理的[[自來水|自來水]]，所處位置鄰近需要供水的地方<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://openlearn.open.ac.uk/mod/resource/view.php?id=185924 |title=Open University – Service Reservoirs |accessdate=2014-05-10 |archive-date=2016-05-16 |archive-url=http://arquivo.pt/wayback/20160516122131/http://openlearn.open.ac.uk/mod/resource/view.php?id=185924 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在西方國家，部份配水庫會以[[水塔|水塔]]的形式興建。在其他地區，配水庫則多數建於地底。而在[[香港|香港]]，很多地底配水庫的上蓋都會地盡其用，興建[[公園|公園]]、[[遊樂場|遊樂場]]或[[球場|球場]]等康樂設施。

[[英國|英國]][[倫敦|倫敦]]近郊的[[貴橡|貴橡]]設有一個[[磚|磚]]砌的配水庫，建於1901年至1909年，曾為全世界最大的配水庫<ref name="Honor Oak Reservoir 1">{{cite web | title = Honor Oak Reservoir | publisher = London Borough of Lewisham | url = http://www.lewisham.gov.uk/SiteCollectionDocuments/ForestHillAndHonorOakSecretsLeaflet.pdf | accessdate = 2011-09-01 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120318025526/http://www.lewisham.gov.uk/SiteCollectionDocuments/ForestHillAndHonorOakSecretsLeaflet.pdf | archivedate = 2012-03-18 }}</ref> ，至今仍是全歐洲最大<ref name="Honor Oak Reservoir 2">{{cite web  | title = Honor Oak Reservoir  | publisher = Mott MacDonald  | url = http://www.projectmanagement.mottmac.com/projects/?mode=type&id=130093  | accessdate = 2011-09-01  | deadurl = yes  | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111209183234/http://www.projectmanagement.mottmac.com/projects/?mode=type&id=130093  | archivedate = 2011-12-09  }}</ref>。

